snippet.title: The Diary - Playthrough - (Part 1)
snippet.description: The Diary is a spin-off to The Letter (which is a horror visual novel). It's coming out on the 24th! I thought I might read The Diary to get ready for The Letter which I can't play even when it comes out so you guys would have to wait. Hopefully it gets us hyped if you like horror vns. qwq I might have also downloaded something random in this video because I didn't bother to read... idk though maybe I did need it. I might also be a bit mad because my family is talking about me....
